1
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was half dead.</font>

2
00:00:13,900 --> 00:00:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I failed yet again to make Lady 
Doux a cruel and vicious demon.</font>

3
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly am I supposed to do?</font>

4
00:00:27,740 --> 00:00:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no.</font>

5
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I'm stuck.</font>

6
00:00:32,730 --> 00:00:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll talk to Yairya about it.</font>

7
00:00:35,550 --> 00:00:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

8
00:00:40,730 --> 00:00:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, all of you!</font>

9
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? What in the world happened?</font>

10
00:00:44,690 --> 00:00:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't be serious.</font>

11
00:00:47,310 --> 00:00:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}YAIRYA – FIRST-CLASS WITCH</font>

12
00:00:47,550 --> 00:00:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yairya!</font>

13
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this rate, we witches are finished...</font>

14
00:00:53,410 --> 00:00:54,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Jahi...</font>

15
00:00:55,620 --> 00:00:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's all your fault.</font>

16
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

17
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE WITCHES' POTIONS WORK WAY TOO GOOD!!</font>

18
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The Witches' Potions 
Work Way Too Good!!"</i></font>

19
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The witches are finished because of us?</font>

20
00:02:39,570 --> 00:02:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean by that?</font>

21
00:02:41,390 --> 00:02:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look at this.</font>

22
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is me...</font>

23
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, His Majesty sent us to</font>

24
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">invade various locations in 
order to unify the demon world.</font>

25
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just it.</font>

26
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

27
00:02:55,650 --> 00:03:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you all expanded our territory,</font>

28
00:02:57,170 --> 00:03:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DEMONS</font>

29
00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">more and more demons 
who were in the castle</font>

30
00:03:02,900 --> 00:03:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">were sent out to various locations 
for development and maintenance...</font>

31
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a result, we ended up having 
to do the work around the castle</font>

32
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the demons were supposed to do!</font>

33
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're supposed to concoct various potions,</font>

34
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we're all exhausted.</font>

35
00:03:20,270 --> 00:03:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're at our limit.</font>

36
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't even know what to say to that...</font>

37
00:03:25,250 --> 00:03:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

38
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I guess I feel bad for you, too.</font>

39
00:03:29,460 --> 00:03:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean by that?</font>

40
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heave ho, heave ho.</font>

41
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Heave ho... Heave ho...</font>

42
00:03:34,340 --> 00:03:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux, what are you doing here?</font>

43
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

44
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One, two, one, two.</font>

45
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweepy sweep.</font>

46
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your trials with Lady Doux 
aren't going well, right?</font>

47
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sweepy sweep.</font>

48
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sweepy, sweepy sweep.</font>

49
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They aren't.</font>

50
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweepy, sweepy sweep.</font>

51
00:03:54,950 --> 00:03:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yairya, I have a favor to ask.</font>

52
00:03:57,500 --> 00:04:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anyone who can make a 
potion that'll make Lady Doux evil?</font>

53
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MUS – JUNIOR WITCH</font>

54
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello!</font>

55
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be Mus. I'm sure Yairya 
has already filled you in, but...</font>

56
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so surprised?!</font>

57
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-B-B-Because I told her that I couldn't 
possibly do this and turned her down.</font>

58
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

59
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't even make a single 
potion? You're finished!</font>

60
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}STAB</font>

61
00:04:27,490 --> 00:04:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll do it! I can do it!</font>

62
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please just give me a little more time!</font>

63
00:04:31,820 --> 00:04:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure... If you'll get right to it...</font>

64
00:04:34,090 --> 00:04:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay!</font>

65
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm...</font>

66
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no official formulation for 
a drug that draws out one's evil.</font>

67
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's someone named Mus that's 
completely self-taught in her research.</font>

68
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only a slight possibility, 
but she might be able to do it.</font>

69
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just she's a bit different...</font>

70
00:04:57,580 --> 00:05:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see... Let's see...</font>

71
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is she actually going 
to be able to do this?</i></font>

72
00:05:03,540 --> 00:05:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's done...</font>

73
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh!</font>

74
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably a bit bitter though.</font>

75
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GURGLE GURGLE GURGLE...</font>

76
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux can eat green peppers, so it's okay!</font>

77
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bitterness aside, 
is this even drinkable?</font>

78
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's made only with things 
good for your body...</font>

79
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

80
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to be more cautious, Lady Doux!</font>

81
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a reaction! Sh-She 
should be evil now.</font>

82
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you feel, Lady Doux?</font>

83
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dummy-ass!</font>

84
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You chicken butt! You macaroon!</font>

85
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux said something rude?!</font>

86
00:05:41,410 --> 00:05:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll krill you!</font>

87
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though she seems to be just a tad off...</font>

88
00:05:45,820 --> 00:05:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we're going in the right direction! 
Can you adjust the formula?</font>

89
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes!</font>

90
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm super angy!</font>

91
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never seen Lady 
Doux like this before.</i></font>

92
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If we continue adjusting the formula...</i></font>

93
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's done. Here.</font>

94
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's about time, you slowypoke!</font>

95
00:06:09,970 --> 00:06:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

96
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wah! She multiplied!</font>

97
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why?!</font>

98
00:06:14,470 --> 00:06:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boom!</font>

99
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's play!</font>

100
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:19,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hungry.</font>

101
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What kind of formula adjustment 
could possibly lead to this?!</font>

102
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!</font>

103
00:06:26,790 --> 00:06:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She should turn back with this!</font>

104
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are so many...</font>

105
00:06:33,090 --> 00:06:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Douxs!</font>

106
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you just complicating 
this even more?!</font>

107
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll adjust it some more!</font>

108
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty!</font>

109
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My eyes are flickering...</font>

110
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This should work.</font>

111
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we're strong!</font>

112
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So close! Now, if she was just evil!</font>

113
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-One more time!</font>

114
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DWAHAHAHA</font>

115
00:06:56,470 --> 00:07:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FWAHAHAHA</font>

116
00:06:58,270 --> 00:07:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, at least her voice 
sounds more evil now.</font>

117
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sorry!</font>

118
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, at least Lady Doux 
returned to her normal self.</font>

119
00:07:10,410 --> 00:07:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sorry...</font>

120
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's calm down a bit. 
Could I get some tea?</font>

121
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right away!</font>

122
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Here you go.</font>

123
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

124
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is this...</font>

125
00:07:32,050 --> 00:07:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a potion!</font>

126
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry! I mistook it for tea!</font>

127
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry! 
I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry!</font>

128
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Why didn't you check more carefully?!</font>

129
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? We've switched bodies?!</font>

130
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now something's been summoned!</font>

131
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! It's a Mr. Octopus! Mr. Octopus!</font>

132
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?!</font>

133
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Curses...</font>

134
00:08:17,690 --> 00:08:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't do anything in this body.</i></font>

135
00:08:21,890 --> 00:08:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, Mus!</font>

136
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something about this!</font>

137
00:08:26,810 --> 00:08:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mus!</font>

138
00:08:31,650 --> 00:08:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make up for this by 
cutting my stomach open!</font>

139
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait no! That's my body!</font>

140
00:08:37,900 --> 00:08:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

141
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:50,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-We're finally back to normal...</font>

142
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:54,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew I couldn't do it...</font>

143
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I could do it!</font>

144
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's so much I don't know even 
when I'm making one potion!</font>

145
00:09:06,010 --> 00:09:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so useless, and all 
I do is cause trouble...</font>

146
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just...</font>

147
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux had a lot of fun though!</font>

148
00:09:16,290 --> 00:09:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

149
00:09:17,570 --> 00:09:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were a lot of me, I transformed, 
and then there was a Mr. Octopus!</font>

150
00:09:22,890 --> 00:09:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can all witches make lots 
of potions this amazing?!</font>

151
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No! I can't even make them 
the way I actually want...</font>

152
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone above me can make potions 
without making a single mistake.</font>

153
00:09:38,330 --> 00:09:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of mine are incomplete or failures.</font>

154
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even today...</font>

155
00:09:46,540 --> 00:09:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's go ask them how 
to make them together.</font>

156
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

157
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I-I couldn't possibly! Even if I go,
 I'm just going to cause trouble!</font>

158
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

159
00:09:58,610 --> 00:10:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}W-W-W-Wait! Lady Doux!</font>

160
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't possibly!</font>

161
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait! No!</font>

162
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you actually went to Mus.</font>

163
00:10:11,170 --> 00:10:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?! Yairya, how dare you?!</font>

164
00:10:13,810 --> 00:10:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess I have no choice.</font>

165
00:10:17,730 --> 00:10:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've brought me this incomplete 
potion to make someone evil,</font>

166
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you must've come to get advice, right?</font>

167
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, uh... yes...</font>

168
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's the case.</font>

169
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just keep messing up and...</font>

170
00:10:32,390 --> 00:10:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it won't go well...</font>

171
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm sure you're busy... And I'm sure 
I'm bothering you... So I'll just...</font>

172
00:10:45,070 --> 00:10:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you squirm anymore,
I'm putting you into a pot.</font>

173
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sorry!</font>

174
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to show me 
something, straighten up.</font>

175
00:10:53,410 --> 00:10:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux, this way.</font>

176
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

177
00:10:57,530 --> 00:10:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey! You're using that here?!</font>

178
00:10:59,950 --> 00:11:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Th-Th-That might be dangerous!</font>

179
00:11:02,310 --> 00:11:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Even if something 
happens, I'm here.</font>

180
00:11:11,430 --> 00:11:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

181
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is...</font>

182
00:11:22,050 --> 00:11:25,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can feel my fatigue melting away.</font>

183
00:11:25,990 --> 00:11:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

184
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really know why, 
but my fatigue's all gone!</font>

185
00:11:30,130 --> 00:11:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same here! My body feels so much lighter!</font>

186
00:11:33,170 --> 00:11:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why? Also, what was 
all that smoke just now?</font>

187
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

188
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone in the castle 
suddenly feels better.</font>

189
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That range of effect is amazing!</font>

190
00:11:45,850 --> 00:11:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um... This is uh...</font>

191
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:52,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could you make something 
like this, Mus?!</font>

192
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek!</font>

193
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's brilliant!</font>

194
00:11:55,210 --> 00:11:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

195
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen a potion like this! 
How in the world did you make it?</font>

196
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! B-But this was a failure...</font>

197
00:12:03,170 --> 00:12:06,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be a failure, 
but it's still amazing!</font>

198
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

199
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mus,</font>

200
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to teach you all kinds of things 
and learn all kinds of things from you!</font>

201
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we teach each other 
things we don't know,</font>

202
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure we'll be able to make 
something even more amazing!</font>

203
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's work together!</font>

204
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, ma'am!</font>

205
00:12:22,590 --> 00:12:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

206
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux, too! Doux wants to learn things!</font>

207
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's make them together, Lady Doux!</font>

208
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:34,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of potion did 
you want to make, Lady Doux?</font>

209
00:12:34,050 --> 00:12:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A super yummy potion 
that you can drink lots of!</font>

210
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I just went through 
all this for nothing...</font>

211
00:12:44,170 --> 00:12:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE HERO IS JUST TOO UNRELIABLE!</font>

212
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The Hero Is Just Too Unreliable!!"</i></font>

213
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came all this way to 
take down the demon king</font>

214
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and somehow got separated 
from my party...</font>

215
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

216
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this situation, I should... Huh?</font>

217
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boom!</font>

218
00:13:18,190 --> 00:13:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello!</font>

219
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait! Who are you?!</font>

220
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd you come from?!</font>

221
00:13:23,570 --> 00:13:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux's name is Doux.</font>

222
00:13:27,070 --> 00:13:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was playing hide-and-seek with Papa</font>

223
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and found a hole and 
slid all the way here.</font>

224
00:13:34,810 --> 00:13:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name, miss?</font>

225
00:13:37,230 --> 00:13:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ur. Ur the Hero.</font>

226
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A hero! Wow!</font>

227
00:13:43,590 --> 00:13:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may be a hero, 
but there're so many of us.</i></font>

228
00:13:46,990 --> 00:13:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, there's basically a hero 
for every village in existence...</i></font>

229
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ahem. I'm looking for my party 
that I've been separated from.</font>

230
00:13:54,350 --> 00:13:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But first, we need to get 
you back up to the surface.</font>

231
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek! A bug!</font>

232
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many giant Mr. Spiders!</font>

233
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't! No one told me there'd 
be bugs that huge here!</font>

234
00:14:13,430 --> 00:14:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There... There has to be 
some solution to this!</font>

235
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

236
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is the <i>Adventurer's Tome</i>!</font>

237
00:14:20,860 --> 00:14:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has all kinds of knowledge and 
tricks needed for adventures.</font>

238
00:14:23,990 --> 00:14:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-There we go!</font>

239
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"For bug-type demons, use 
sweet things or hellfire"?!</font>

240
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have anything sweet!</font>

241
00:14:31,380 --> 00:14:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I need to be able to use powerful 
magic to produce hellfire.</font>

242
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux knows how.</font>

243
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really?</font>

244
00:14:36,930 --> 00:14:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flare!</font>

245
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not a very big flame!</font>

246
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're gathering to the light!</font>

247
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's no use! There's 
just too many of them!</font>

248
00:14:47,610 --> 00:14:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Look!</font>

249
00:14:49,210 --> 00:14:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right! Sweet things!</font>

250
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, if we just use this...</font>

251
00:14:56,650 --> 00:14:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was a demon, too!</font>

252
00:14:59,470 --> 00:15:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course there wouldn't be strawberries 
growing in a place like this!</font>

253
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is probably an earth-type. 
How do I deal with this?</font>

254
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strawberry!</font>

255
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux! Look up how to deal with 
these earth-type demons for me!</font>

256
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

257
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"How to make strawberry tarts"...</font>

258
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Doux!</font>

259
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Okay, it says to use 
water for earth-type demons.</font>

260
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux has some!</font>

261
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wait, you can use 
water-based magic, too?!</font>

262
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

263
00:15:32,450 --> 00:15:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just water!</font>

264
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux! No, these are...</font>

265
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They gave me a strawberry!</font>

266
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These were <i>actually</i> strawberries?! 
What's the right answer here?!</font>

267
00:15:49,530 --> 00:15:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}"ADVENTURE, ADVENTURE!"
LYRICS: KANATA NAKAMURA
 COMPOSITION AND ARRANGEMENT: YURI MORITA
SONG: DOUX</font>

268
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Adventure, adventure, it's 
time for an adventure</i></font>

269
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Deep, deep down a pitfall</i></font>

270
00:16:08,170 --> 00:16:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's look over here and look over there</i></font>

271
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's see everything that's down here</i></font>

272
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go! Go! Go, go, go!</i></font>

273
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go! Go! Go, go, go!</i></font>

274
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'm down here with my friend</i></font>

275
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}So it's not scary at all</i></font>

276
00:16:34,970 --> 00:16:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Adventure, adventure, it's 
time for an adventure</i></font>

277
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Deep, deep down a pitfall</i></font>

278
00:16:43,250 --> 00:16:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's look over here and look over there</i></font>

279
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's see everything that's down here</i></font>

280
00:16:51,610 --> 00:16:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go! Go! Go, go, go!</i></font>

281
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go! Go! Go, go, go!</i></font>

282
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'm down here with my friend</i></font>

283
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}So it's not scary at all</i></font>

284
00:17:19,430 --> 00:17:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like we were able to 
at least lose the demons.</font>

285
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

286
00:17:28,260 --> 00:17:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-My book!</font>

287
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

288
00:17:30,460 --> 00:17:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux, don't worry.</font>

289
00:17:34,110 --> 00:17:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This demon...</font>

290
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no doubt about it.</font>

291
00:17:37,670 --> 00:17:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the demon who sent me and 
my friends flying and separated us.</font>

292
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful!</font>

293
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this thing goes berserk, 
we won't be able to deal with...</font>

294
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux! W-Wait!</font>

295
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you...</font>

296
00:17:52,370 --> 00:17:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was eaten!</font>

297
00:17:54,130 --> 00:17:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-N-No! I-I need to hurry and save her!</font>

298
00:17:57,790 --> 00:18:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But my <i>Adventurer's Tome</i>...</font>

299
00:18:02,010 --> 00:18:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There it is!</font>

300
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what to do with a demon 
like that unless the book tells me...</font>

301
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough!</font>

302
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always relying on that 
dumb book! This is a battlefield!</font>

303
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't make your own decisions,</font>

304
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can't protect those
you want to protect!</font>

305
00:18:21,590 --> 00:18:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're right.</font>

306
00:18:22,570 --> 00:18:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm... I'm...</font>

307
00:18:26,290 --> 00:18:27,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a hero!</font>

308
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:35,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that! Doux!</font>

309
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whee!</font>

310
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

311
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux, are you hurt?</font>

312
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got it!</font>

313
00:18:45,910 --> 00:18:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

314
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a stick!</font>

315
00:18:48,810 --> 00:18:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, this was stuck in their throat!</font>

316
00:18:57,190 --> 00:19:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were probably thrashing 
around because it hurt so bad.</font>

317
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why you went into its mouth?!</font>

318
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But how did you know that 
was inside their throat?</font>

319
00:19:07,660 --> 00:19:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just had a hunch.</font>

320
00:19:09,090 --> 00:19:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-A hunch?!</font>

321
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... it could've swallowed you whole.</font>

322
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You tried to save it</font>

323
00:19:16,210 --> 00:19:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without the <i>Adventurer's Tome</i> 
or any actual solution...</font>

324
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you did that, too!</font>

325
00:19:21,370 --> 00:19:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

326
00:19:21,930 --> 00:19:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You saved me even without the book.</font>

327
00:19:26,840 --> 00:19:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been relying on that 
book this whole time...</i></font>

328
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That </i>Adventurer's Tome<i> was given to 
me by my father, who was a great hero.</i></font>

329
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He recorded everything he learned 
and experienced on his adventures.</i></font>

330
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's filled with his desire for me 
to become a full-fledged hero...</i></font>

331
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so weak... that without that book...</i></font>

332
00:19:52,710 --> 00:19:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I don't rely on that book, I didn't 
think I could protect anything.</i></font>

333
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

334
00:19:59,080 --> 00:20:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Ur!</font>

335
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We finally found you!</font>

336
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those voices...</font>

337
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My party's here!</font>

338
00:20:06,220 --> 00:20:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're getting the heck outta here!</font>

339
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they brought something 
insane with them?!</font>

340
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-W-W-Wait a m-minute! What is that?!</font>

341
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea! But it's probably 
the boss of this dungeon!</font>

342
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:22,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our weapons and magic
don't do anything to it!</font>

343
00:20:22,190 --> 00:20:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this rate, it's gonna catch up to us!</font>

344
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! We're gonna die!</font>

345
00:20:29,690 --> 00:20:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

346
00:20:31,690 --> 00:20:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys! Look after her for me.</font>

347
00:20:33,580 --> 00:20:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll buy you some time!</font>

348
00:20:35,330 --> 00:20:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you saying, Ur?!</font>

349
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! And you don't even 
have your <i>Adventurer's Tome</i>!</font>

350
00:20:40,910 --> 00:20:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay!</font>

351
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys and Doux have opened my eyes!</font>

352
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even without that book...</i></font>

353
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can protect others!</i></font>

354
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think there was a hole in the forest 
that connected to this dungeon.</font>

355
00:21:13,700 --> 00:21:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking for you, Doux!</font>

356
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No way...</font>

357
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that...</font>

358
00:21:20,090 --> 00:21:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demon King Ahriman?!</font>

359
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's he doing here?!</font>

360
00:21:24,020 --> 00:21:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa!</font>

361
00:21:26,470 --> 00:21:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Papa"?!</font>

362
00:21:28,150 --> 00:21:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux! I'm so sorry! 
You must've been so lonely!</font>

363
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope! The hero saved me, so I was fine.</font>

364
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Is that so?</font>

365
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-What's going on here, Ur?!</font>

366
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why were you with the 
demon king's daughter?!</font>

367
00:21:45,650 --> 00:21:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Uh, I had no idea...</font>

368
00:21:47,950 --> 00:21:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hero's party.</font>

369
00:21:50,350 --> 00:21:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you've come this far, you 
must've come to defeat me.</font>

370
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE HERO'S PARTY'S PERSPECTIVE</font>

371
00:21:55,410 --> 00:21:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To thank you for taking 
care of Doux for me,</font>

372
00:21:57,810 --> 00:21:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll let you have a go 
at me. So come at me.</font>

373
00:21:59,990 --> 00:22:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No thanks!</font>

374
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, well that's no fun.</font>

375
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye!</font>

